DcodeIDE Installation & Usage Guide
-----------------------------------
1. Download the latest release files:
   - DcodeIDE.7z
   - DcodeIDE.pck
2. Extract DcodeIDE.7z using 7-Zip (recommended).
   - This will give you DcodeIDE.exe 
3. Place DcodeIDE.pck in the same folder as DcodeIDE.exe.
   - The executable will automatically load the .pck when run.
4. Run DcodeIDE.exe directly.
   - DcodeIDE.exe is a standalone build.
Notes:
- Works on Windows (64-bit).
- Keep DcodeIDE.exe and DcodeIDE.pck together in the same directory.
- For updates, check the GitHub Releases page or CHANGELOG.md.
- If antivirus flags the file, it is a false positive due to compression.
